title: TEAM FOR FAMILY NIGHT CLUB TOURNEMENT

embed.description: FAMILY LEGENDS SERIES 2016 - LEAGUE OF LEGENDS COMPETITION Fancy yourself a LEGEND? Try your chances at the Family Legends Series 5 vs 5 LEAGUE OF LEGENDS competition! Playing SOLO or in a TEAM?

body:
Hey guys so you may not know already but in brisbane a local club in fortitude valley is holding a tournament. Very valuable prizes which include a training session with THE CHIEFS. I am very serious about this but i am unable to make a team as my players live else where. If you are willing to train as much before hand then send me a message. If your not willing to give it your all then dont bother messaging me. 

Good luck.
